         print(f[0m[2m"[Worker[0m[2m {worker[0m[2m_id}][0m[2m job {[0m[2mjob['[0m[2mid']}[0m[2m failed:[0m[2m {e[0m[2m}")
     ```[0m[2m
     
     The[0m[2m job status[0m[2m stays "[0m[2mprocessing"[0m[2m forever ([0m[2mor rather[0m[2m, it[0m[2m was[0m[2m set[0m[2m to "[0m[2mprocessing"[0m[2m in dequeue[0m[2m,[0m[2m and[0m[2m never gets[0m[2m changed[0m[2m).[0m[2m That's[0m[2m why[0m[2m they[0m[2m disappear from[0m[2m the queue[0m[2m (not[0m[2m pending[0m[2m,[0m[2m so not[0m[2m picked[0m[2m up again[0m[2m) and[0m[2m don't show[0m[2m as failed[0m[2m.
     
